Panzer::
Stil off line.

DarkMouse::
 She felt the tail bash into her side. As she fell to the ground,"YOU 
Burnt My Tail!" THUMP!
DarkMouse got up and brushed the dirt off her backside.  She lifted 
up her tail and looked at the painfully charred tip.  She sighed 
deeply and lowered her head. "Well, war is never a beautiful thing. 
My tail is a casualty." under her breath.  She looked up as the 
dragons grabbed the cat. With a ring of fire around her, she couldn't 
go after them. "Galvatron. I could use a bit of back up here. 
Neptune, your assistance would be appreciated."
She looked at the ring of fire,"I got to hand it to those lizards. 
They do know how to fight fire with fire."
realizing that she had lost the cat to them and now Galvatron would 
probably be dissappointed in her.
